				<h1>Interesting Security Links</h1>
<p>
If you want to harden your Linux System please check out the following links:
<br/>

<ul>
<li><a href="https://benchmarks.cisecurity.org/">CIS security benchmarks provide very good hardening guides for many important open source components (like Apache, Tomcat, etc)</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.bsi.bund.de/DE/Home/home_node.html">The BSI is a German Security Institution (Government)</a> </li>
<li><a href="https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Category:OWASP_Top_Ten_Project">OWASP Top 10</a></li>
</ul>

<br/>
